name: KALYANAM KAROTI MATHURA
briefDescription: Kalyanam Karoti organization  was served  154049 disabled people out of which 79053 were provided  with artificial limbs , Examined total 802587 eye  patients out of which  137172 patients got successful surgical treatment which is about 17% of the covered population . Also served 26839 polio patients out of which 7563 (28.13% of total covered population ) got successful treatment
